Installation for UNIX like systems:

1. Install Poly/ML 5.5 (http://www.polyml.org/download.html).

2. Edit the Makfile: change the LIBPATH variable so that it points to your
   Poly/ML libraries and select the appropriate POLYLIB line for your platform.
   Then do

  $ make

3. Make sure the bin/l3 shell script has execute permission. And move the
   files in bin/ to your preferred location.

4. To start L3, type l3.
